28
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:09,120
When can we go to your wedding?

29
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:13,200
Here. A toast to both of you.

30
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:14,400
Congratulations.

31
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,080
Cheers.

32
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:26,760
Come on, guys.

33
