Life is really fun.

37
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:44,280
I remember what happened on the ice rink

38
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:46,440
like it was yesterday.

39
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:48,480
That year,

40
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:50,840
Chunsheng painted a portrait,

41
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:52,720
had a fight,

42
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,240
and chased a girl.

43
00:03:54,320 --> 00:03:55,920
I finally realized

44
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,720
that he did everything for you.

45
00:03:58,880 --> 00:04:00,600
I was so dumb that I was thinking,

46
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:02,480
"Could anyone pursue a girl

47
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:04,080
in someone else's name?"

48
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,640
Well, yes.

49
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:21,760
What's wrong with you?

50
00:04:22,520 --> 00:04:24,000
Can't drinking shut you up yet?

51
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,040
Hongling, ignore him.

52
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:34,320
When are you getting married?

53
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:40,880
Hongling and I haven't discussed it yet.

54
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:42,840
