55
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:44,280
After we're back in the army.

56
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:44,800
Then...

57
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:45,560
Not that late.

58
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:53,400
Guohua and I have been
together for years.

59
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:54,840
No need to wait anymore.

60
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:57,360
In a day or two.

61
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,760
When you're all here in Beijing,

62
00:04:58,760 --> 00:04:59,880
we'll get married.

63
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,840
Do come to our wedding.

64
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,400
What do you say, Guohua?

65
00:05:27,840 --> 00:05:29,000
Hongling is so real.

66
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:30,280
She hasn't changed at all.

67
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:31,600
On the ice rink,

68
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,640
Hongling was the...

69
