76
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:51,120
No, I'm afraid.

77
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:51,920
It's open.

78
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:55,120
Why is it not?

79
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:58,520
Then let's go skating tomorrow.

80
