00:06:28,980 --> 00:06:33,020
(Unit One)

91
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:40,000
Guohua.

92
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,560
How's everything going in the army?

93
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,000
Not bad.

94
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,680
Just so-so, nothing special.

95
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:48,840
How are you doing?

96
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:54,280
Look.

97
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:57,240
I can walk now.

98
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:59,880
