99
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:02,400
You'll get better.

100
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:06,520
Yeah.

101
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:09,120
I have to be patient.

102
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:12,360
I'm lucky enough to get back on my feet.

103
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,120
Thanks to Xiaomei.

104
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:19,280
You and Xiaomei...

105
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:20,400
Is it true that you're together?

106
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:22,240
What are you talking about?

107
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,080
How could it not be true?

108
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,480
It's true, with no doubt.

109
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,280
Good.

110
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:29,360
Glad to know that.

111
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:31,600
Guohua,

112
00:07:32,280 --> 00:07:33,400
do you remember

113
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:35,080
I told you about a girl

114
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:37,000
in the stack room?

115
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,240
Stack room?

116
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:42,080
Oh, I remember.

117
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:44,040
You said you wanted to pursue her.

118
00:07:49,200 --> 00:07:51,240
That girl is Xiaomei?

119
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:58,480
Xiaomei knew it a long time ago.

120
00:07:59,080 --> 00:08:00,440
But I was too dumb

121
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:02,080
to know it all the time.

122
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:04,680
Then how did you recognize her?

123
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:06,960
She accompanied me
when I returned to Beijing,

124
00:08:08,080 --> 00:08:09,160
had the operation,

125
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:10,880
and did the rehabilitation.

126
00:08:12,400 --> 00:08:13,840
If I still hadn't recognized her,

127
00:08:14,440 --> 00:08:15,880
I would be too ungrateful.

128
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,240
Wish you a nice life with Hongling.

129
00:08:53,900 --> 00:08:59,020
(Qianhai Beiyan)

130
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:37,760
Where's Hongling?

131
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:40,160
She's back home to fetch something.

132
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:41,240
Chunsheng...

133
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,880
Why haven't he and Xiaomei come?

134
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,120
They said they would come soon

135
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,000
and asked us to play

136
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:45,840
instead of waiting for them.

137
00:10:19,280 --> 00:10:20,080
What's wrong?

138
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:26,880
Where's Xiao Chunsheng?

139
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:57,400
Will you skate or not?

140
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:01,320
Then what did you come here for?

141
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:17,760
You saw them, huh?

142
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,960
What? Happy?

143
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:23,360
Are you done talking?

144
00:11:31,400 --> 00:11:33,200
Yanqiu, Tian.

145
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:33,840
Where's Guohua?

146
00:11:38,560 --> 00:11:39,560
I'll go for them.

147
00:11:51,760 --> 00:11:52,400
Chunsheng.

148
00:11:54,400 --> 00:11:55,160
Xiaomei.

149
00:11:59,880 --> 00:12:00,600
Guohua,

150
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:02,720
since I left the army,

151
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:04,800
I haven't got any information.

152
00:12:04,920 --> 00:12:07,280
Tell me something about it, OK?

153
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:09,720
Go.

154
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,000
Shall we skate?

155
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:33,400
Go.

156
00:12:44,800 --> 00:12:45,960
Funny.

157
00:12:50,320 --> 00:12:51,680
Sometimes, I think

158
00:12:52,160 --> 00:12:53,800
we have a bone.

159
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:56,080
Look.

160
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,000
We're never

161
00:12:58,680 --> 00:12:59,960
the leading roles.

162
00:13:00,760 --> 00:13:01,840
At a party,

163
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:03,040
in the army,

164
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:04,800
or even on the ice rink,

165
00:13:05,920 --> 00:13:06,640
we're always

166
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:09,320
the supporting roles.

167
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:11,760
Spotlight

168
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:14,040
always follows them.

169
00:13:15,160 --> 00:13:15,840
You and I

170
00:13:16,680 --> 00:13:18,160
have to stay in the shadow.

171
00:13:28,960 --> 00:13:30,480
You skate as well as before.

172
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:33,360
Not at all.

173
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:49,440
Why didn't you chase me?

174
00:13:52,760 --> 00:13:54,360
Xiaomei doesn't like to skate too fast.

175
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:55,960
So, I'm used to skating slowly.

176
00:14:02,120 --> 00:14:03,560
Now that you're worried,

177
00:14:05,520 --> 00:14:07,200
why did you let them skate alone?

178
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:15,920
Because today,

179
00:14:16,920 --> 00:14:19,320
I have something important to tell you.

180
00:14:29,920 --> 00:14:30,560
Listen.

181
00:14:31,280 --> 00:14:32,280
The same old song.

182
00:14:40,120 --> 00:14:41,200
It has the same melody.

183
00:14:42,040 --> 00:14:42,920
But it's not

184
00:14:43,880 --> 00:14:45,080
the old same song.

185
00:14:49,720 --> 00:14:50,400
Chunsheng,

186
00:14:52,040 --> 00:14:52,960
I'm getting married.

187
00:14:56,880 --> 00:14:57,760
Do you get it?

188
00:14:58,320 --> 00:14:59,360
I'm getting married.

189
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:07,560
Guohua,

190
00:15:08,560 --> 00:15:09,800
I'm now a doctor.

191
00:15:10,120 --> 00:15:10,880
Did you know?

192
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:13,120
Not until now.

193
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:14,200
Congratulations.

194
00:15:14,200 --> 00:15:15,440
I used to be a nurse.

195
00:15:15,800 --> 00:15:16,720
You must be aware, right?

196
00:15:16,720 --> 00:15:17,480
Yes.

197
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:20,080
Before,

198
00:15:20,560 --> 00:15:22,120
I longed to be a doctor

199
00:15:22,920 --> 00:15:24,120
because I thought

200
00:15:24,560 --> 00:15:27,000
a nurse only took care of patients

201
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:29,040
and looked less decent than a doctor.

202
00:15:29,560 --> 00:15:30,560
Like you said,

203
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:32,960
nurses are supporting roles

204
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:35,120
and the spotlight doesn't follow them.

205
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:37,120
But,

206
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:39,920
when I become a doctor,

207
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,320
I realized

208
00:15:42,080 --> 00:15:43,040
that nursing care

209
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:45,240
is very important.

210
00:15:46,680 --> 00:15:48,040
When I was a nurse,

211
00:15:48,320 --> 00:15:49,960
I considered everything for the patients.

212
00:15:50,720 --> 00:15:51,560
Was the ward

213
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:53,960
ventilative or noisy?

214
00:15:54,480 --> 00:15:56,080
What would patients have for lunch?

215
00:15:56,360 --> 00:15:58,200
How often should the bedding be changed?

216
00:15:58,480 --> 00:16:00,080
A lot of trifles.

217
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:02,480
When I served as a doctor,

218
00:16:02,960 --> 00:16:05,600
I found out such trifles

219
00:16:05,800 --> 00:16:06,760
shaped me.

220
00:16:07,240 --> 00:16:08,920
So, in any case,

221
00:16:09,560 --> 00:16:12,200
I give the top priority to patients.

222
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:15,360
As far as I see,

223
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:17,720
I'm not only treating them,

224
00:16:18,360 --> 00:16:19,920
but also taking care of them

225
00:16:20,680 --> 00:16:22,440
so that they can live in the hospital

226
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:23,920
with as much dignity as they can enjoy.

227
00:16:26,560 --> 00:16:29,360
But what if I was a doctor
in the beginning?

228
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:31,480
What if I was the leading role

229
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:33,240
when the story began?

230
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:34,720
Then in my mind,

231
00:16:35,040 --> 00:16:36,240
I'm afraid,

232
00:16:36,880 --> 00:16:38,320
I would only long to be promoted

233
00:16:38,800 --> 00:16:39,960
and get more powerful.

234
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:41,680
I would want the spotlight on me.

235
00:16:43,680 --> 00:16:45,480
Then, I can't be what I am now.

236
00:16:48,640 --> 00:16:49,600
So, Guohua,

237
00:16:50,680 --> 00:16:53,040
it's sometimes just an issue of timing.

238
00:16:53,600 --> 00:16:54,680
At the right time,

239
00:16:55,360 --> 00:16:56,240
it doesn't matter

240
00:16:56,960 --> 00:16:58,600
whether you have the spotlight.

241
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:03,080
Staying in the shadow
would be even cooler.

242
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:04,040
Right?

243
00:17:06,760 --> 00:17:08,310
It's so clear-headed of you.

244
00:17:11,800 --> 00:17:13,110
Let me ask you something.

245
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:15,240
Do you really trust him that much?

246
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:27,800
Xiao Chunsheng,

247
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:29,960
you dumped me with a letter.

248
00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:31,880
Do you want to pretend nothing happened?

249
00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:32,920
I won't.

250
00:17:34,800 --> 00:17:35,480
Hongling,

251
00:17:36,240 --> 00:17:37,000
I loved you.

252
00:17:38,240 --> 00:17:39,560
I would never deny that.

253
00:17:40,320 --> 00:17:40,920
Then you...

254
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:42,120
But what's gone is gone.

255
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:47,080
Look.

256
00:17:47,960 --> 00:17:49,400
Just like this place.

257
00:17:50,240 --> 00:17:51,520
When we were young,

258
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:53,240
we often skated here.

259
00:17:54,880 --> 00:17:56,400
But now, we seldom come.

260
00:17:58,240 --> 00:18:00,120
It doesn't mean
this place no longer matters.

261
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:02,320
But in our lives,

262
00:18:02,760 --> 00:18:04,120
something else matters more.

263
00:18:06,160 --> 00:18:07,400
Are you sure it's Tong Xiaomei?

264
00:18:20,120 --> 00:18:21,880
If it was me who got on the train,

265
00:18:21,880 --> 00:18:23,200
would everything be different?

266
00:18:23,560 --> 00:18:24,280
Hongling,

267
00:18:24,720 --> 00:18:25,800
no buts.

268
00:18:27,080 --> 00:18:28,400
Like I said,

269
00:18:28,920 --> 00:18:29,640
we made

270
00:18:30,360 --> 00:18:31,760
our own choices.

271
00:18:32,600 --> 00:18:33,680
After choosing what we want,

272
00:18:34,800 --> 00:18:35,720
don't regret it.

273
00:18:37,120 --> 00:18:38,120
Don't look back.

274
00:18:48,800 --> 00:18:49,440
Go.

