♪Where I watch the tide ebb and flow♪

295
00:20:23,050 --> 00:20:26,770
♪May love warm all waiting men♪

296
00:20:28,760 --> 00:20:30,160
Let's go home.

297
00:20:31,800 --> 00:20:35,270
♪May the world be fantastic as always♪

298
00:20:35,270 --> 00:20:39,850
♪Casting its blue sunshine on the sea♪

299
00:20:41,600 --> 00:20:42,200
We should go.

300
00:20:42,360 --> 00:20:43,000
See you.

301
00:21:19,840 --> 00:21:22,440
The snow scene here is gorgeous.

302
00:21:24,960 --> 00:21:25,680
Do you like it?

303
00:21:27,440 --> 00:21:28,080
Yes.

304
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:31,520
I grew up in the military compound

305
00:21:31,760 --> 00:21:32,880
and I'm fed up.

306
00:21:34,080 --> 00:21:35,480
It's great to live here.

307
00:21:36,040 --> 00:21:38,560
The houses are close

308
00:21:38,920 --> 00:21:40,840
and the neighbors are nice.

309
00:21:42,600 --> 00:21:43,400
Here,

310
00:21:44,320 --> 00:21:47,240
I feel calm and secure.

311
00:21:52,920 --> 00:21:53,600
Chunsheng.

312
00:21:54,920 --> 00:21:55,800
Actually,

313
00:21:57,360 --> 00:21:58,720
I don't skate very well.

314
00:22:00,520 --> 00:22:02,040
You skated well last time.

315
00:22:04,120 --> 00:22:05,720
Because you were holding my hand.

316
00:22:13,840 --> 00:22:14,920
I would always hold your hand.

317
00:22:21,760 --> 00:22:23,160
Teach me to skate.

318
00:22:26,680 --> 00:22:27,160
I won't.

319
00:22:28,640 --> 00:22:29,640
Why not?

320
00:22:30,640 --> 00:22:31,600
Why won't you teach me?

321
00:22:37,880 --> 00:22:38,960
Say something.

322
00:22:41,840 --> 00:22:42,760
My silly girl.

323
00:22:43,960 --> 00:22:44,960
What?

324
00:22:45,800 --> 00:22:47,280
What's wrong with you?

325
00:22:47,280 --> 00:22:48,640
Why didn't you answer me?

326
00:22:53,600 --> 00:22:55,040
Why won't you teach me?

327
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:57,920
Come on.

328
00:23:01,400 --> 00:23:02,040
So much dust.

329
00:23:07,040 --> 00:23:07,840
What a surprise!

330
00:23:08,720 --> 00:23:09,920
This room hasn't changed at all.

331
00:23:11,160 --> 00:23:11,960
Yeah.

332
00:23:23,360 --> 00:23:24,400
It's still here.

333
00:23:24,400 --> 00:23:25,580
(Dictionary of Chinese Pharmacy)

334
00:23:26,960 --> 00:23:28,000
I really miss it.

335
00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:35,760
I remember

336
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:37,040
when I was reading here,

337
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:38,280
I wondered

338
00:23:38,280 --> 00:23:40,640
who also read here.

339
00:23:41,280 --> 00:23:43,840
So, it was you, my girl.

340
00:23:45,760 --> 00:23:46,280
Right.

341
00:23:46,840 --> 00:23:48,160
That was me.

342
00:23:49,080 --> 00:23:50,920
What? Unsatisfied?

343
00:23:52,120 --> 00:23:53,400
No, no.

344
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:54,920
I'm very satisfied.

345
00:23:57,120 --> 00:23:58,120
Actually,

346
00:23:58,600 --> 00:23:59,840
I didn't see you clearly.

347
00:24:00,520 --> 00:24:01,720
I just saw

348
00:24:02,400 --> 00:24:03,200
someone

349
00:24:04,080 --> 00:24:05,240
flitting by.

350
00:24:05,840 --> 00:24:07,200
But I was sure

351
00:24:07,640 --> 00:24:10,000
it must be a pretty girl.

352
00:24:13,240 --> 00:24:14,040
Come on.

353
00:24:14,640 --> 00:24:16,080
Don't be honey-lipped.

354
00:24:17,560 --> 00:24:18,160
Leaving?

355
00:24:19,880 --> 00:24:20,560
Are you angry?

356
00:24:22,520 --> 00:24:23,840
I'm not angry.

357
00:24:24,960 --> 00:24:26,640
You didn't say that back then.

358
00:24:28,840 --> 00:24:30,120
What did I say?

359
00:24:31,440 --> 00:24:32,440
I can't remember.

360
00:24:33,440 --> 00:24:35,080
How about you remind me?

361
00:24:39,280 --> 00:24:42,240
Fine, fine. My fault.

362
00:24:42,440 --> 00:24:43,560
I was wrong.

363
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:46,880
I lied to you.

364
00:24:50,200 --> 00:24:50,840
About that?

365
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:52,320
I told you

366
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:55,360
I saw that girl was He Hongling.

367
00:24:56,920 --> 00:24:57,680
I lied.

368
00:24:59,440 --> 00:25:00,200
I know.

369
00:25:02,200 --> 00:25:03,360
Because you...

370
00:25:04,720 --> 00:25:06,120
You loved her.

371
00:25:06,800 --> 00:25:09,440
Right. That's why I lied.

372
00:25:12,800 --> 00:25:13,720
I understand.

373
00:25:22,360 --> 00:25:23,240
But actually,

374
00:25:25,160 --> 00:25:26,640
I knew she wasn't the girl
a long time ago.

375
00:25:29,080 --> 00:25:29,920
In recent years,

376
00:25:30,880 --> 00:25:32,400
I've been having the same dream.

377
00:25:33,320 --> 00:25:34,120
In the dream,

378
00:25:35,120 --> 00:25:36,920
I was chasing a girl.

379
00:25:37,440 --> 00:25:38,560
I kept chasing her

380
00:25:40,040 --> 00:25:41,600
as if I was chasing my dream.

381
00:25:44,320 --> 00:25:45,360
But never could I

382
00:25:45,880 --> 00:25:47,000
see her face.

383
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:49,320
Every time I thought

384
00:25:49,320 --> 00:25:50,600
I could catch up with her,

385
00:25:52,160 --> 00:25:53,160
she disappeared.

386
00:25:56,600 --> 00:25:57,520
Until one day...

387
00:26:03,560 --> 00:26:04,600
I finally saw her.

388
00:26:05,370 --> 00:26:10,010
♪Snow falls on this page♪

389
00:26:13,860 --> 00:26:18,570
♪I fail to see the face in my dream♪

390
00:26:21,840 --> 00:26:22,440
Xiaomei.

391
00:26:22,460 --> 00:26:27,500
♪Get to the seaside beneath the stars♪

392
00:26:30,650 --> 00:26:36,190
♪Pick up the fallen bookmark♪

393
00:26:37,470 --> 00:26:44,520
♪I'll spend years with you♪

394
00:26:45,850 --> 00:26:53,860
♪Watching flowers bloom in the valley♪

395
00:26:54,240 --> 00:26:58,100
♪As vigorously♪

396
00:26:58,200 --> 00:26:59,440
Do you know what I thought

397
00:27:00,200 --> 00:27:01,520
the moment I woke up?

398
00:27:02,440 --> 00:27:03,400
What?

399
00:27:08,080 --> 00:27:09,000
I thought, "I'm so glad it's you."

400
00:27:19,360 --> 00:27:20,880
So, I want to tell you this.

401
00:27:22,440 --> 00:27:24,160
It's not because you came
back to Beijing with me

402
00:27:24,760 --> 00:27:25,720
and accompanied me in rehabilitation

403
00:27:26,520 --> 00:27:27,440
that I fell in love with you.

404
00:27:28,560 --> 00:27:29,360
Maybe earlier.

405
00:27:31,080 --> 00:27:32,880
Even before I realized it,

406
00:27:34,200 --> 00:27:35,400
I was in love with you.

407
00:27:41,120 --> 00:27:42,200
Qi Tian is right.

408
00:27:42,880 --> 00:27:43,840
He said, I appear

409
00:27:44,080 --> 00:27:46,000
to be fearless of anything.

410
00:27:47,040 --> 00:27:49,400
But actually, I fear to face inward.

411
00:27:51,120 --> 00:27:52,000
And when

412
00:27:52,800 --> 00:27:54,880
someone is scared of something,

413
00:27:55,280 --> 00:27:57,600
he avoids it subconsciously
instead of facing it.

414
00:27:59,480 --> 00:28:00,480
It was my problem.

415
00:28:01,800 --> 00:28:02,760
Over all these years,

416
00:28:03,520 --> 00:28:05,200
I didn't dare to face it

417
00:28:07,880 --> 00:28:09,280
so that you had to

418
00:28:10,080 --> 00:28:11,800
wait in silence all alone.

419
00:28:13,260 --> 00:28:17,320
♪With you♪

420
00:28:18,410 --> 00:28:25,540
♪Watching flowers bloom in the valley♪

421
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:26,400
Xiaomei,

422
00:28:27,360 --> 00:28:28,640
since I came back from the army,

423
00:28:29,320 --> 00:28:31,040
I've figured out many things.

424
00:28:32,840 --> 00:28:34,280
When there's something I should bear

425
00:28:34,280 --> 00:28:36,000
or something I have to do,

426
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:38,120
I'll try my best to do it.

427
00:28:40,360 --> 00:28:41,080
Do you get it?

428
00:28:43,840 --> 00:28:50,050
♪I'll spend years with you♪

429
00:28:51,200 --> 00:28:52,200
Look at you.

430
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:53,840
Laughing and crying at the same time.

431
00:28:54,320 --> 00:28:55,160
My silly girl.

432
00:28:56,340 --> 00:29:00,330
♪Bloom in the valley♪

433
00:29:00,660 --> 00:29:08,720
♪As vigorously as how we first met♪

434
00:29:08,890 --> 00:29:11,900
♪The courage of guarding♪

435
00:29:11,900 --> 00:29:17,100
♪Keeps out all the loneliness♪

436
00:29:17,640 --> 00:29:18,400
Xiaomei,

437
00:29:23,240 --> 00:29:24,200
let's get married.

438
00:30:10,140 --> 00:30:14,380
(Wedding)

439
00:32:52,240 --> 00:32:55,600
(How time flew in Beijing.)

440
00:32:57,480 --> 00:33:01,560
(Xiao Chunsheng and Tong Xiaomei
got closer and closer.)

441
00:33:04,080 --> 00:33:06,200
(Ye Guohua and He Hongling)

442
00:33:07,160 --> 00:33:09,440
(had a grand wedding)

443
00:33:10,120 --> 00:33:11,320
(before going back to the army.)

444
00:33:13,640 --> 00:33:15,320
(On different positions,)

