00:33:16,280 --> 00:33:17,820
(they worked hard respectively.)

446
00:33:17,820 --> 00:33:18,770
About face!

447
00:33:19,060 --> 00:33:19,800
About face!

448
00:33:19,800 --> 00:33:20,790
Left face!

