00:33:21,400 --> 00:33:23,240
(No one stopped improving himself.)

450
00:33:24,160 --> 00:33:25,120
(Every one of them)

451
00:33:25,560 --> 00:33:28,240
(kept growing like pliable widow branches)

452
00:33:29,160 --> 00:33:31,440
(in early spring of Beijing.)

453
00:33:40,100 --> 00:33:44,340
(Beijing Railway Station)

454
00:33:58,440 --> 00:33:59,040
Xiaoliu.

455
00:33:59,320 --> 00:33:59,840
Xiang Dong.

456
00:33:59,840 --> 00:34:00,600
Chunsheng.

457
00:34:07,800 --> 00:34:08,600
Let me look at you.

458
00:34:10,320 --> 00:34:11,320
You got tanned, Xiaoliu.

459
00:34:11,630 --> 00:34:12,230
What about me?

460
00:34:13,150 --> 00:34:13,880
Xiang Dong,

461
00:34:14,520 --> 00:34:15,760
why do you look thinner?

462
00:34:16,600 --> 00:34:18,520
You two are so late.

463
00:34:18,710 --> 00:34:20,280
The rest of us are waiting.

464
00:34:20,280 --> 00:34:20,920
We're back now.

465
00:34:21,320 --> 00:34:21,880
Chunsheng,

466
00:34:22,360 --> 00:34:23,880
are your legs OK now?

467
00:34:24,440 --> 00:34:25,670
Yes. I've recovered.

468
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:27,400
Chunsheng,

469
00:34:27,630 --> 00:34:28,880
we're all together again.

470
00:34:29,190 --> 00:34:30,320
Let's go on to roar in Beijing.

471
00:34:31,600 --> 00:34:32,280
Come on.

472
00:34:33,280 --> 00:34:34,710
What are your plans?

473
00:34:36,600 --> 00:34:37,920
We'll wait for assigned jobs.

474
00:34:38,320 --> 00:34:39,840
If we can't get a job,

475
00:34:39,840 --> 00:34:41,480
we'll do some small business like Tian.

476
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:41,880
Right.

477
00:34:41,880 --> 00:34:42,440
OK.

478
00:34:42,800 --> 00:34:44,190
That's not bad.

479
00:34:45,280 --> 00:34:46,230
If you need my help,

480
00:34:46,230 --> 00:34:46,800
let me know.

481
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:47,360
Don't hesitate to tell me.

482
00:34:47,360 --> 00:34:48,120
OK, Chunsheng.

483
00:34:48,230 --> 00:34:49,000
We won't hesitate.

484
00:34:49,520 --> 00:34:50,150
All right, let's go.

485
00:34:50,150 --> 00:34:50,710
- Go.
- Let's go home.

486
00:34:50,710 --> 00:34:51,080
Come on, Chunsheng.

487
00:34:51,080 --> 00:34:51,840
- I'll carry it myself.
- Come on.

488
00:34:52,040 --> 00:34:52,520
Go.

489
00:35:05,000 --> 00:35:07,080
(After Xiaohui became the leading model,)

490
00:35:07,680 --> 00:35:09,200
(she was too busy with fashion shows)

491
00:35:09,880 --> 00:35:10,960
(to go home.)

492
00:35:12,120 --> 00:35:15,440
(Heizi got suspicious again.)

493
00:35:21,320 --> 00:35:21,960
Anyone in?

494
00:35:21,960 --> 00:35:22,680
Open the door!

495
00:35:22,720 --> 00:35:23,320
Coming!

496
00:35:24,040 --> 00:35:25,360
I'm Xiaohui's colleague.

497
00:35:25,480 --> 00:35:27,080
Is this where Xiao Chunsheng lives?

498
00:35:27,520 --> 00:35:28,040
Yes.

499
00:35:28,400 --> 00:35:30,520
Heizi and his men
smashed our presentation.

500
00:35:30,520 --> 00:35:32,200
Xiaohui sent me to Xiao Chunsheng,

501
00:35:32,200 --> 00:35:33,320
saying he could stop them.

502
00:35:38,880 --> 00:35:39,520
Where are they?

503
00:35:39,840 --> 00:35:40,400
There.

504
00:35:40,400 --> 00:35:41,600
Out they come.

505
00:35:41,680 --> 00:35:42,720
He's the attacker.

506
00:35:44,720 --> 00:35:45,480
Heizi!

507
00:35:46,800 --> 00:35:47,440
It's him.

508
00:35:47,920 --> 00:35:48,520
Get in the car.

509
00:35:59,600 --> 00:36:01,040
That man was terrible.

510
00:36:01,040 --> 00:36:02,280
In front of so many people,

511
00:36:02,280 --> 00:36:04,000
he rushed onto the stage
and punched Xiaohui hard.

512
00:36:04,000 --> 00:36:05,440
He even tried to strip her!

513
00:36:05,440 --> 00:36:06,880
She wasn't wearing too much.

514
00:36:07,080 --> 00:36:07,720
Where's Xiaohui?

515
00:36:07,960 --> 00:36:09,080
In the dressing room.

516
00:36:09,200 --> 00:36:10,160
She doesn't see anyone.

517
00:36:10,560 --> 00:36:11,600
I'll go check on her.

518
00:36:11,600 --> 00:36:12,160
OK.

519
00:36:15,160 --> 00:36:16,000
Xiaohui.

520
00:36:16,840 --> 00:36:18,720
Xiaohui, it's me, Yanqiu.

521
00:36:21,000 --> 00:36:21,680
Come in.

522
00:36:25,920 --> 00:36:26,560
Xiaohui.

523
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:37,360
Yanqiu,

524
00:36:37,880 --> 00:36:39,480
when he's out of the detention house,
give this to him.

525
00:36:41,280 --> 00:36:42,240
What's this?

526
00:36:48,300 --> 00:36:51,780
(Divorce Agreement)

527
00:37:30,800 --> 00:37:31,560
Beat him!

528
00:37:33,040 --> 00:37:33,720
Heizi,

529
00:37:34,600 --> 00:37:35,680
do you want to marry me?

530
00:37:36,400 --> 00:37:36,960
Yes.

531
00:37:38,240 --> 00:37:39,280
Even dreamed of that.

532
00:38:03,920 --> 00:38:04,360
Xiaohui.

533
00:38:05,440 --> 00:38:06,240
Xiaohui, Xiaohui.

534
00:38:06,480 --> 00:38:07,360
Stop, Xiaohui.

535
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:09,560
Xiaohui.

536
00:38:10,440 --> 00:38:12,840
Heizi did the wrong thing
and should learn his lesson.

537
00:38:13,680 --> 00:38:15,040
You want a divorce and I won't stop you.

538
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:17,600
But shouldn't you

539
00:38:18,160 --> 00:38:19,800
talk to him when he gets out

540
00:38:20,120 --> 00:38:21,200
before divorcing him?

541
00:38:21,840 --> 00:38:23,080
Marriage is between a couple.

542
00:38:23,520 --> 00:38:24,480
So is divorce.

543
00:38:24,960 --> 00:38:26,960
You should put an end together.

544
00:38:27,480 --> 00:38:28,440
I am putting an end.

545
00:38:30,760 --> 00:38:31,200
Yanqiu,

546
00:38:31,840 --> 00:38:32,760
look at my face.

547
00:38:33,360 --> 00:38:34,680
Look at it.

548
00:38:36,400 --> 00:38:37,360
It's been so many years.

549
00:38:38,160 --> 00:38:39,520
I don't know what he thinks of me.

550
00:38:40,120 --> 00:38:41,280
But I know

551
00:38:41,440 --> 00:38:43,160
I've been very loyal to him!

552
00:38:44,360 --> 00:38:45,040
Yes, yes.

553
00:38:45,080 --> 00:38:47,120
We all know that. So does Heizi.

554
00:38:47,760 --> 00:38:49,240
These years, those men...

555
00:38:49,360 --> 00:38:49,800
Right.

556
00:38:50,520 --> 00:38:50,960
That's right.

557
00:38:51,840 --> 00:38:52,800
Some men wanted to pursue me.

558
00:38:53,440 --> 00:38:54,520
Some wanted to make out with me.

559
00:38:55,200 --> 00:38:56,400
Some women even told me

560
00:38:56,960 --> 00:38:57,880
when picking a man,

561
00:38:58,320 --> 00:39:00,320
we should pick handsome

562
00:39:00,440 --> 00:39:00,920
and cool guys,

563
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:03,160
or rich guys

564
00:39:03,360 --> 00:39:05,000
who had great power.

565
00:39:05,360 --> 00:39:06,400
They seemed to think

566
00:39:06,800 --> 00:39:08,560
a woman had to get a man like that.

567
00:39:10,160 --> 00:39:11,680
But I'm not that kind of woman.

568
00:39:12,320 --> 00:39:13,840
Right. We know that.

569
00:39:13,960 --> 00:39:14,400
Never mind.

570
00:39:14,520 --> 00:39:15,600
I don't bother to argue with them.

571
00:39:21,280 --> 00:39:21,680
Yanqiu,

572
00:39:23,440 --> 00:39:24,200
over all these years,

573
00:39:24,880 --> 00:39:25,680
you've witnessed everything.

574
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:30,200
He and I often fought.

575
00:39:34,720 --> 00:39:35,280
Do you know

576
00:39:36,240 --> 00:39:37,760
how we got to know each other?

577
00:39:39,760 --> 00:39:42,160
I remember you said

578
00:39:42,160 --> 00:39:43,440
you saved Heizi.

579
00:39:45,680 --> 00:39:46,320
Near Bayi Lake.

580
00:39:48,400 --> 00:39:51,000
That year, a boy fell into the lake.

581
00:39:51,440 --> 00:39:52,080
He jumped to save him.

582
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:54,680
He must have been an idiot.

583
00:39:55,520 --> 00:39:56,800
